.:: Zebra puzzle ::.
The people prefer 5 different types of sport: cricket, skiing, rowing, cycling, soccer
There are 5 different nationalities: english, spanish, ukranian, norwegian, japanese
The people grow 5 different varities of flowers: azalea, aconite, sunflower, zinnia, balloon-flower
There are 5 different favourite beverages: coffee, tea, milk, orange-juice, water
The people prefer 5 different music-genres: soul, techno, house, classical, funk

1. the english is the person who's sport is cricket
2. the spanish is the fan of soul
3. the person drinking coffee is the person who's sport is skiing
4. the ukranian is the person drinking tea
5. the person who's sport is skiing is to the right of the person who's sport is rowing
6. the person who growsazalea is the fan of funk
7. the person who growsaconite is the person who's sport is cycling
8. the person drinking milk is in the middle
9. the norwegian is on the far left
10. the person who growssunflower is on the left or right of the fan of techno
11. the person who growsaconite is to the left or right of the fan of classical
12. the person who growszinnia is the person drinking orange-juice
13. the japanese is the person who growsballoon-flower
14. the norwegian is to the left or right of the person who's sport is soccer

.:: Answer ::.
